UPDATE `quest_template` SET
    `OfferRewardText` = 'He was a good goblin, young Scrimshank.  Let''s hope that his demise was not in vain by what he was able to record with his surveying equipment.$B$BIt seems as though we have quite the situation on our hands here with these bugs.  They''re way too cunning for their own good, and the research we''ve done so far is shaping up to indicate that they might even be under the controlling influence of a third party!  If this is the case, then it bodes ill for not only Gadgetzan, but the whole desert!',
    `RequestItemsText` = 'Well, what news do you have?  You look like you''ve been in quite the fight... is Scrimshank alive?'
