    `OfferRewardText` = '<King Magni Bronzebeard is visibly upset.>$B$BIt seems that even in death, Thaurissan has won.$B$BYou are dismissed, $N. Before you leave, you may choose your reward from the royal vault.$B$B<King Bronzebeard slumps into his throne to mull over this bizarre change of events.>',
