    `OfferRewardText` = 'Cauldron Lord Soulwrath''s key disintegrates as it touches the lock on the access panel at the base of the cauldron''s platform. A slight clanking noise is heard within, and the access panel swings open to reveal more viscous toxins within the cauldron''s framework.$B$BThere is a small spigot that the bottle fits well enough under, allowing you to draw a sample for Shadow Priestess Vandis back at the Bulwark.',
