    `RequestItemsText` = 'A Corruptor''s Scourgestone is the insignia of the Scourge''s overlords.  A powerful being that holds a position of authority over the Scourge will always possess one.  To slay such a malevolent creature would surely advance the cause of the Argent Dawn, and all good causes!$B$BOn behalf of the Argent Dawn, I will give you a valor token in exchange for just a single one of these insignia.  Use caution in acquiring one, $N - such powerful beings are not to be trifled with.'
