    `OfferRewardText` = '"And so it begins. Father Cenarius. And so it begins."$B$BDendrite makes a quick, invisible gesture in the air above him. A slight aura of power falls over him.$B$B"The first perspective of nature you must adapt to is that of the bear. I will put you on the path to understanding this aspect of druidic life, but it is you that must embrace it and propagate it - now and forever!"',
