    `OfferRewardText` = 'You have learned all I can teach you, $N. May the blessings of the Earthmother guide you in choosing a pet.$B$BHere you are, $N. I will now give you the power to tame a beast, as well as call it and dismiss it as you see fit. Use your new skills with pride and honor the Earthmother.',
    `RequestItemsText` = 'You will soon be ready, $N.'
