    `OfferRewardText` = 'Wonderful! We thank you for your generous donation, $N!',
    `RequestItemsText` = 'Mageweave is running low, and we could use your help to replenish our stocks!  By counting on the community as a whole, we would only need a donation of 60 pieces of mageweave cloth from you to enable us to reach our goal.  Such generosity would not go unnoticed by Orgrimmar, I assure you!$B$BIf you have the sixty pieces of mageweave cloth on you and are ready to donate them, I''m able to take them from you now.'
