    `OfferRewardText` = 'Excellent! Let''s perform the trade then. It''s hard to part with this excellent armor, but I''m afraid I won''t be needing it any time soon.$B$BIf you''re interested in performing more work for me, I might be willing to give up the rest of the pieces.',
    `RequestItemsText` = 'Have you brought me what I requested of you, $N?'
