    `OfferRewardText` = 'By the light, what is that! This is what tormented me for months? I... I think I remember those eyes, yes.$B$BAs much as it pains me to do so, I must show this to Rose. There is no other way to prove what she means to me, that I would never do what she thinks I did!$B$BAnd your name, friend? Ah, thank you $N.',
